{
  "stem": "10768.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was born in Przysietnica near Brzozow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was there, pampered by my paternal grandfather and by all aunts and uncles who were still single at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I really had a very lovely childhood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After my brother was born-- and Mother was always busy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She kept, was kept busy at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was always dealing with something when the business was not very good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was providing milk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was buying milk and butter from peasants and selling it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So somebody came to help with, let's say, my brother, who was after me, Abraham.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or grandmother, who lived in the same house, came sort of to help out and babysit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was older, when I came home and there were already five children, I even remember that Mother gave me the responsibility of taking care of the youngest to diaper her or to, to put her to sleep in a little wooden-- what do you call that?",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A little cradle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grandmother was already at that time older, and she couldn't always, let's say, take care.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had responsibilities very frequently at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lesko was a town-- of course, there was never a census-- but approximately there were 2,000 Polish and Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were between 4,000 and 5,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jews were predominantly small merchants-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how shall I say-- tailors, cabinet makers, trade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They trade.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Gentiles were always on the, the official, the officials in the offices.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Jews hardly ever-- we had, I think, two Jewish doctors, which nobody even knew that they were Jewish, because they were not associated with the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was one or two Jewish lawyers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, they were very progressive.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
